==Japanese==
===Adjective===
'''二つ''' ([[ふたつ]], ''futatsu'')

# [[two]] [small items or things without a counter category]
#: 二つ (ふたつ, ''futatsu'') is only used when the items counted have no specific counter category. See [[w:Japanese counter word|Wikipedia's "Japanese counter word" entry]] for details.

